{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requestProgress","title":"requestProgress","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/requestProgress":{"abstract":[{"text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"title":"requestProgress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackState/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressCh